# 🗺️ SindicApp Development Plan - Two-Stage Approach

## 📋 **STAGE 1: AI TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION**
*Core technical infrastructure, features, and functionality that can be implemented by AI*

---

## **✅ Phase 0: Base Project Setup** *(COMPLETED)*

### 🔧 Initial Setup
- [x] **Folder Structure**: Create monorepo architecture
  - [x] `/frontend` (Next.js + TypeScript)
  - [x] `/backend` (Express.js + TypeScript)  
  - [x] `/shared` (Shared types)
  - [x] `/database` (Schemas and migrations)
  - [x] `/docs` (Technical documentation)

- [x] **Frontend Configuration**:
  - [x] Next.js 14 setup with App Router
  - [x] Strict TypeScript configuration
  - [x] Tailwind CSS + base components setup
  - [x] ESLint + Prettier configuration
  - [x] Zustand for state management

- [x] **Backend Configuration**:
  - [x] Express.js with TypeScript setup
  - [x] Folder structure (routes, controllers, middleware, services)
  - [x] CORS and basic security middleware
  - [x] Development scripts configuration

- [x] **Database**:
  - [x] PostgreSQL local setup
  - [x] Prisma ORM configuration
  - [x] Basic initial schema
  - [ ] Redis cache setup

- [x] **Initial DevOps**:
  - [ ] Docker setup for development
  - [x] Development and build scripts
  - [x] Environment variables setup

---

## **✅ Phase 1: Authentication and Base User** *(COMPLETED)*

### 🔐 Authentication System
- [x] **Base User Models**:
  - [x] Prisma schema for User, Role, Session
  - [x] Initial migrations
  - [x] Basic seeders

- [x] **Backend Auth**:
  - [x] JWT + Refresh Token implementation
  - [x] Authentication middleware
  - [x] Endpoints: register, login, logout, refresh
  - [x] Zod validation

- [x] **Frontend Auth**:
  - [x] Login/register pages
  - [x] Form components
  - [x] Authentication context/store
  - [x] Route protection

- [x] **User Profile**:
  - [x] Basic profile CRUD
  - [ ] Avatar upload
  - [x] Privacy settings

- [x] **Roles and Permissions**:
  - [x] Basic role system (user, moderator, admin)
  - [x] Authorization middleware
  - [x] Frontend guards

---

## **✅ Phase 2: Core Business Logic** *(COMPLETE)*

### 🏢 Business Entities ✅
- [x] **Company Models**:
  - [x] Schema for Company, Industry, Location
  - [x] API for automatic company registration
  - [x] Business data validation

- [ ] **Google Maps Integration**:
  - [ ] Google Maps API setup
  - [ ] Interactive map component
  - [ ] Company geolocation
  - [ ] Location-based search

- [x] **Company Profiles**:
  - [x] Automatic company pages
  - [x] Public vs private information
  - [x] Company verification system

### 💬 Forum System ✅
- [x] **Forum Models**:
  - [x] Schema for Forum, Thread, Post, Comment
  - [x] Company/sector categorization
  - [x] Moderation system

- [x] **Forum API**:
  - [x] Complete CRUD for forums
  - [x] Threading system
  - [x] Search and filters
  - [x] Optimized pagination

- [x] **Forum Frontend**:
  - [x] Forum list with search and filtering
  - [x] Post list with engagement features
  - [x] Professional UI with responsive design
  - [x] Real-time like/comment interactions

---

